snippet.title: Funko Fusion - NOPE Reveal Trailer
snippet.description: Get ready to face Jean Jacket and play as the Haywood's from NOPE for the first time in Funko Fusion. We're thrilled to have the chance to revisit Haywood's Hollywood Horses Ranch and Jupiter's Claim!
